CatDescriptText: Headline for related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 28, 1958, page A11, reads: "Alphas Host Brilliant 30th Anniversary Ball"
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing light colored strapless ball gown with sash and jeweled decoration at waist, shoes, and carrying light colored clutch, standing on exterior steps of Hotel Webster Hall for the Alpha Phi Alpha 30th Anniversary ball
